cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use BehaviorGuard in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "BehaviorGuard: Context-Aware Anomaly Detection in Conversational AI"
abstract: >
  BehaviorGuard is an LLM-native anomaly detection framework that detects
  anomalous user requests by modeling per-user behavioral patterns across
  semantic, linguistic, and temporal dimensions. It maintains privacy-preserving
  user profiles from interaction histories and computes multi-dimensional anomaly
  scores to drive tiered response policies.
authors:
